Oh? You again!

43
00:04:39,404 --> 00:04:41,281
You can't go in.

44
00:04:41,281 --> 00:04:42,423
What?

45
00:04:42,423 --> 00:04:45,051
Are you going to do a club activity this late at night?

46
00:04:45,051 --> 00:04:47,596
I know that there is no club meeting today.

47
00:04:47,596 --> 00:04:49,272
Get out of my way.

48
00:04:49,272 --> 00:04:50,732
No can do!

49
00:04:50,732 --> 00:04:52,392
Get out of my way!

50
00:04:52,392 --> 00:04:54,352
I will not!

51
00:04:54,352 --> 00:04:56,830
Why do you keep coming to this school? Huh?

52
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:59,381
What trouble are you going to cause?

53
00:04:59,381 --> 00:05:01,635
I won't, please move aside.

54
00:05:01,635 --> 00:05:02,619
No.

55
00:05:02,619 --> 00:05:05,330
Outsiders aren't allowed in the school premises for a reason.

56
00:05:05,330 --> 00:05:07,489
You can't go in.

57
00:05:11,936 --> 00:05:13,713
Come on!

58
00:05:14,705 --> 00:05:16,074
Just five minutes.

59
00:05:16,074 --> 00:05:17,793
No, it'll take just one minute.

60
00:05:17,818 --> 00:05:21,945
I don't care. You can't go in.

61
00:05:21,945 --> 00:05:24,165
You can't go in.

62
00:05:24,165 --> 00:05:26,475
Leave now!

63
00:05:26,475 --> 00:05:27,524
Is she not answering her phone?
[Ah Ra]

64
00:05:27,548 --> 00:05:28,907
She's been unreachable all day.
[Ji Seong]

65
00:05:28,907 --> 00:05:30,109
I saw her at school earlier.
[Yu Seol]

66
00:05:30,133 --> 00:05:32,406
Are you going to see Kim Yeon Du?
[Se Hui]

67
00:05:38,505 --> 00:05:40,272
Hey! Stop!

68
00:05:40,272 --> 00:05:42,424
Hey, you punk!

69
00:05:43,176 --> 00:05:45,661
Man, this is brand new.

70
00:05:45,661 --> 00:05:47,404
Hey!

71
00:05:59,468 --> 00:06:01,452
Have you seen Kim Yeon Du?

72
00:06:01,452 --> 00:06:02,721
Yeon Du?

73
00:06:02,721 --> 00:06:04,773
Didn't she go to find some book?

74
00:06:04,773 --> 00:06:06,716
Yes, I think she went down to the basement.

75
00:06:06,716 --> 00:06:09,560
The message told her to go to the basement.

76
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:11,453
The basement?

77
00:06:13,857 --> 00:06:15,525
Who is he, by the way?

78
00:06:15,525 --> 00:06:17,509
I don't know.

79
00:06:17,509 --> 00:06:19,645
Yeon Du!

80
00:06:19,645 --> 00:06:21,730
Kim Yeon Du!

81
00:06:21,730 --> 00:06:23,532
Where is she?

82
00:06:25,135 --> 00:06:28,303
Kim Yeon Du! Where are you?

83
00:06:54,748 --> 00:06:56,765
Kim Yeon Du!

84
00:07:10,847 --> 00:07:11,840
Yeon Du.

85
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:13,541
Kim Yeon Du!

86
00:07:22,934 --> 00:07:26,570
[Medicine: Kim Yeon Du]
[Take two a day for three days.]

87
00:07:50,579 --> 00:07:53,707
Yeon Du, is it true that you're dating Senior Ye Seok?
[WHYNOT TALK: Mi Yeon]

88
00:07:53,707 --> 00:07:57,210
Since when? Why didn't you tell us?
[Su Jeong]

89
00:07:57,210 --> 00:08:01,110
Wow! She said it wasn't true but it is true?
[Sol Hui]

90
00:08:23,294 --> 00:08:25,613
Headache...

91
00:08:28,375 --> 00:08:31,800
Why are you here?

92
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:34,805
Hyeon Ho, how come you're here?

93
00:08:48,737 --> 00:08:50,730
Your fever is down.

94
00:08:51,765 --> 00:08:54,074
Wait here.

95
00:09:18,024 --> 00:09:20,126
I know you have no appetite, but try to eat.

96
00:09:20,126 --> 00:09:22,536
So you can take your medicine.

97
00:09:28,843 --> 00:09:33,694
Do you remember what happened yesterday?

98
00:09:33,694 --> 00:09:35,574
Yesterday?

99
00:09:43,792 --> 00:09:47,122
Hello? Anyone there?

100
00:09:47,988 --> 00:09:50,005
Hello?

101
00:09:52,075 --> 00:09:53,801
Yes.

102
00:09:54,811 --> 00:10:00,095
Did anything happen between you and Jin Se Hui yesterday?

103
00:10:00,725 --> 00:10:02,810
Saehee?

104
00:10:03,970 --> 00:10:06,830
Do you even know where she is?

105
00:10:07,616 --> 00:10:09,650
Go.

106
00:10:09,650 --> 00:10:11,052
Well...

107
00:10:11,052 --> 00:10:14,239
Did she contact you before you got locked in the darkroom?

108
00:10:14,264 --> 00:10:17,358
Or were you supposed to meet her near the darkroom?

109
00:10:18,893 --> 00:10:25,782
Do you think it was Se Hui's fault that I got stuck in the darkroom?

110
00:10:25,782 --> 00:10:28,736
No, I'm just...

111
00:10:29,638 --> 00:10:31,756
It was just an accident.

112
00:10:31,756 --> 00:10:34,600
Se Hui would never do that.

113
00:10:35,593 --> 00:10:38,587
I didn't even see her yesterday.

114
00:10:41,791 --> 00:10:44,869
Don't suspect her.

115
00:10:47,238 --> 00:10:50,123
Okay, go ahead and eat.

116
00:11:03,171 --> 00:11:06,674
If you feel so bad, let me stay with you today.

117
00:11:06,674 --> 00:11:08,184
What?

118
00:11:09,176 --> 00:11:11,771
Do as I say today.

119
00:11:11,771 --> 00:11:13,973
Don't push me away.

120
00:11:20,230 --> 00:11:24,324
If the ex-boyfriend, ex-girlfriend thing makes you uncomfortable...

121
00:11:27,061 --> 00:11:31,430
Then let's say you're a patient and I'm your guardian. Okay?

122
00:11:35,929 --> 00:11:38,422
Go ahead and eat before it gets cold.

123
00:12:36,765 --> 00:12:38,566
Stay in bed and rest.

124
00:12:38,566 --> 00:12:40,084
Call me if you need anything.

125
00:12:40,084 --> 00:12:42,369
What are you going to do?

126
00:12:50,917 --> 00:12:52,620
Why are you changing the light bulb all of a sudden?

127
00:12:52,620 --> 00:12:54,840
I changed it recently.

128
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:56,242
You're scared of the darkness.

129
00:12:56,242 --> 00:13:01,552
I'm changing it now so that it doesn't go out when you're alone.

130
00:13:01,552 --> 00:13:05,657
And it's flickering right now. Hot!

131
00:13:05,657 --> 00:13:08,728
Are you hurt? Are you okay?

132
00:13:08,728 --> 00:13:12,550
I'm fine. I was just kidding.

133
00:13:12,550 --> 00:13:15,710
♫ You know I'm getting closer ♫

134
00:13:15,710 --> 00:13:18,370
♫ Run faster toward me ♫

135
00:13:18,370 --> 00:13:20,949
Why are you changing the door lock code?

136
00:13:20,949 --> 00:13:24,703
You're supposed to change it frequently.

137
00:13:24,703 --> 00:13:26,222
Six digits?

138
00:13:26,222 --> 00:13:28,348
No, eight digits.

139
00:13:28,348 --> 00:13:32,035
But eight digit codes are too easy.

140
00:13:32,035 --> 00:13:35,247
Yeah, it needs to be at least 12 digits.

141
00:13:35,247 --> 00:13:38,249
Give me 12 numbers.

142
00:13:38,249 --> 00:13:40,378
I can't memorize a 12-digit code.

143
00:13:40,403 --> 00:13:43,290
You can.

144
00:13:43,290 --> 00:13:45,620
♫ Like being possessed by something ♫

145
00:13:45,620 --> 00:13:47,670
Tell me the numbers.

146
00:13:47,670 --> 00:13:51,000
♫ I really wanna like you ♫

147
00:13:57,962 --> 00:13:59,672
You haven't gone home?

148
00:13:59,697 --> 00:14:03,650
Not "haven't," but I couldn't.

149
00:14:04,335 --> 00:14:07,338
I have to write a letter of explanation because of some guy.

150
00:14:08,230 --> 00:14:09,666
A letter of explanation?

151
00:14:09,666 --> 00:14:13,019
I told him, so many times, he couldn't come in.

152
00:14:13,019 --> 00:14:18,398
But he pushed me, ran inside anyway, and dared to break the doorknob.

153
00:14:20,276 --> 00:14:23,987
But Yeon Du had happened to collapse in that room...

154
00:14:23,987 --> 00:14:26,522
What? What did you say?

155
00:14:26,522 --> 00:14:27,650
What?

156
00:14:27,650 --> 00:14:31,126
Yeon Du collapsed? When?

157
00:14:31,126 --> 00:14:33,064
Oh, um... Yesterday.

158
00:14:33,064 --> 00:14:37,043
In the darkroom downstairs that your club used to use but was shutdown.

159
00:14:37,068 --> 00:14:39,762
She was found collapsed there.

160
00:14:39,762 --> 00:14:44,366
It seemed she was shocked by getting locked in the room and it made her collapse.

161
00:14:45,794 --> 00:14:47,778
Why was Yeon Du in the darkroom?

162
00:14:47,778 --> 00:14:50,360
He went to save Yeon Du...

163
00:14:57,563 --> 00:14:59,157
Where did he go? Hey!

164
00:14:59,157 --> 00:15:01,558
Ye Seok! Where are you going?

165
00:15:02,789 --> 00:15:05,579
No one listens to me.

166
00:15:06,656 --> 00:15:08,857
Thank you for looking after me today.

167
00:15:10,284 --> 00:15:13,128
Get home safely.

168
00:15:13,128 --> 00:15:15,340
Kim Yeon Du.

169
00:15:15,340 --> 00:15:16,999
Yes?

170
00:15:17,717 --> 00:15:22,660
Are you dating Do Ye Seok?

171
00:15:22,660 --> 00:15:24,764
What?

172
00:15:24,764 --> 00:15:28,293
I accidentally read your friend messages.

173
00:15:31,189 --> 00:15:33,799
Are you really dating him?

174
00:15:38,046 --> 00:15:39,996
No.

175
00:15:41,174 --> 00:15:44,151
It's just a false rumor.

176
00:15:44,151 --> 00:15:47,246
I'm not dating Senior Ye Seok.

177
00:15:50,500 --> 00:15:52,326
Okay, then.

178
00:15:52,935 --> 00:15:55,336
Date me.

179
00:15:55,336 --> 00:15:57,214
What?

180
00:15:57,214 --> 00:15:58,991
Let's date.

181
00:16:00,426 --> 00:16:02,553
Let's start over.

182
00:16:08,393 --> 00:16:10,361
I'm not just saying it.

183
00:16:10,386 --> 00:16:12,596
I'm not joking either.

184
00:16:13,356 --> 00:16:15,816
I'm asking you to be my girlfriend.

185
00:16:15,816 --> 00:16:18,368
I want to start over with you.

186
00:16:23,216 --> 00:16:25,001
Hyeon Ho, I—

187
00:16:25,026 --> 00:16:27,402
I'll do better.

188
00:16:28,329 --> 00:16:31,390
I won't make you cry ever again, I promise.

189
00:16:50,700 --> 00:16:52,500
[Organic Porridge]

190
00:17:03,714 --> 00:17:05,658
It's time for the lesson.

191
00:17:05,658 --> 00:17:06,589
What is this?

192
00:17:06,589 --> 00:17:10,790
Ji Seong wants to take lessons on a tablet too.

193
00:17:16,630 --> 00:17:23,670
♫ The two of us that seems 100 percent close and perfect ♫

194
00:17:23,670 --> 00:17:25,661
I won't make you cry ever again, I promise.
[Best Mistake 3]

195
00:17:25,661 --> 00:17:27,521
Do you know how I feel right now?
[Next episode]

196
00:17:27,521 --> 00:17:31,742
Love is all about timing.

197
00:17:31,742 --> 00:17:33,027
Don't do anymore.

198
00:17:33,027 --> 00:17:36,063
Give up chasing your crush.

199
00:17:36,063 --> 00:17:37,598
What do you mean?

200
00:17:37,598 --> 00:17:41,539
Ah Hun is on another level now.

201
00:17:41,539 --> 00:17:44,120
I think Ji Seong disappeared.

202
00:17:44,120 --> 00:17:45,581
Where is he?

203
00:17:45,581 --> 00:17:47,941
You can look forward to it.

204
00:17:47,941 --> 00:17:49,350
It'll be a lot of fun.

205
00:17:49,350 --> 00:17:52,300
♫ 100 percent between the two of us ♫

206
00:17:52,300 --> 00:17:57,540
♫ Sometimes I know or don't know, it's strange ♫

207
00:17:57,540 --> 00:18:01,038
[Best Mistake 3]
